detaileddescription.para:
This function is mostly useful with control displaying short amounts of text that can be edited by the user, e.g. wxTextCtrl, wxComboBox, wxSearchCtrl etc. Typically it is used to size these controls for the maximal amount of input they are supposed to contain, for example: //Createacontrolforpostcodeentry.
wxTextCtrl*postcode=newwxTextCtrl(this,...);

//Andsetitsinitialandminimalsizetobebigenoughfor
//entering5digits.
postcode->SetInitialSize(
postcode->GetSizeFromTextSize(
postcode->GetTextExtent("99999")));

Also note that you need to escape the following special characters: 


Special character 
Escape as  



&  
